==车站概要==
本站位于昭觉寺南路，沿路呈南北向布置，于2016年7月31日启用<ref name="启用">{{cite news  | title = 成都地铁3号线一期工程试运营 熊猫主题列车首发  | publisher = 新浪  | date = 2016-07-31  | url = http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2016-07-31/doc-ifxunuyk4220798.shtml  | accessdate = 2016-07-31  | language = zh  | archive-date = 2016-08-01  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160801212833/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2016-07-31/doc-ifxunuyk4220798.shtml  | dead-url = no  }}</ref>，因所在路名而得名。在3号线建设期间，本站曾使用工程名“驷马桥北站”<ref>{{cite news| title =成都地铁3号线一期获批 长19.96公里车站15座| publisher =腾讯大成网| date =2012-04-27| url =http://cd.qq.com/a/20120427/000003.htm| accessdate =2012-04-27| language =zh| archive-date =2019-11-06| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20191106124353/https://cd.qq.com/a/20120427/000003.htm| dead-url =no}}</ref><ref >{{cite news| title =地铁3号线施工 驷马桥站和驷马桥北站交通组织方案发布(组图)| publisher =网易| date =2012-04-23| url =http://news.163.com/12/0423/20/7VQ79B6C00014AEE.html| accessdate =2012-04-23| language =zh| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20171209100103/http://news.163.com/12/0423/20/7VQ79B6C00014AEE.html| archive-date =2017-12-09| dead-url =yes}}</ref>。

